---
description:
Standard UI states for all screens.

alwaysApply: true
---

# Required States

Every screen must implement:

Loading

Empty

Error

Offline

Success

---

# Loading

Prefer skeleton screens.

Avoid indefinite spinners.

---

# Empty

Explain why content is empty.

Provide one clear action.

---

# Error

Explain the issue.

Offer retry.

---

# Offline

Show cached data when possible.

Provide sync status.

---

# Cursor Instructions

Never ship a screen without all required states.